summary: Your party are the descendants of the original mighty heroes of the calamity, the ones who sealed away the betrayer gods from...
body: Your party are the descendants of the original mighty heroes of the calamity, the ones who sealed away the betrayer gods from the world. It seems that somehow, those seals are being broken, and only the bloodlines that sealed them are capable of doing so again. Only problem is your blood is also what sets them free. Human sacrifices are a tough business in this day and age.
